yingyinNormal.zh: 现代的却不一样了，都是私人的，由各级别贷款打包而成。

yingyinNormal.en: So this is your private hideout?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是你的秘密基地？

yingyinNormal.en: Skipper, look! I see you, Private.
yingyinNormal.zh: 老大，看啊！看见你了，菜鸟。

yingyinNormal.en: Get me Raymond on the private line.
yingyinNormal.zh: 用我的私人线路打给Raymond。

yingyinNormal.en: What? You put a homing device on Private?
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？你们在菜鸟身上安了跟踪设备？

yingyinNormal.en: No reason. I keep private things in there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有为什么，我把私人物品放在那里。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll be in my own private air conditioning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我自己独享私人空调。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Polmar, let's talk in private. Shall we? Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 波尔马先生，我们单独谈谈，可以吗？好。

yingyinNormal.en: You point that death ray away from Private right now!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你快把那杀伤性射线从菜鸟身上移开。

yingyinNormal.en: Private! Oh! Guys! You're in for it now, Dave! Really?!
yingyinNormal.zh: 菜鸟！哦，兄弟们！你现在怕了吧，戴夫！真的吗？！

yingyinNormal.en: Eggsy, I need to have a private conversation. You're dismissed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾格西，我要和哈利单独谈几句，你回避一下。

yingyinNormal.en: Because I'm too busy answering everybody's private requests for advice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为我正回复每个人的私信，给他们提建议，没空烦恼。

yingyinNormal.en: Private Doss is praying for you. Who the hell is Private Doss?
yingyinNormal.zh: 列兵多斯在为你祈祷？列兵多斯到底是谁？

yingyinNormal.en: This way please, for your private elevator. We have a private elevator?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这边是您的私人电梯，我们有私人电梯。

yingyinNormal.en: Now move your private, Private Parts. Move it. You son of an exhibitionist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在放开你的私处，列兵帕兹。行动。你这个裸露崽子。

yingyinNormal.en: Can we talk in private? Please, yes. I'll be right back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们能借一步说话吗？好的，走吧。我马上就回来。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, I have a lot going on, and I'm a very private person.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听着，我有很多事情要做，而且我是个注重隐私的人。

yingyinNormal.en: No, wait. Private, no. We don't know what that will do to you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，等等，菜鸟！我们不知道那玩意对你有什么影响！

yingyinNormal.en: It's too risky, Private. It already made you sprout a butt-hand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这太冒险了，菜鸟。它都让你屁屁长手了！

yingyinNormal.en: All right! The ray. It works! It works. Private! Are you okay? Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧！射线！起作用了！起作用了！菜鸟，你还好吗？嗯！

examination_example.sentence_trans: 2009年，美国公共部门工会成员的数量超过了私营部门工会成员的数量。

examination_example.sentence: In Britain, more than half of public-sector workers but only about 15% of <highlight>private</highlight>-sector ones are unionized.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在英国，超过一半的公共部门员工加入了工会，但只有大约15%的私营部门员工加入了工会。

examination_example.sentence: In New Zealand, a 206 <highlight>private</highlight> members' Bill tried to permit firms and high-income employees to contract out of the unjustified dismissal regime.

examination_example.sentence: And it should: Wasted time is a drag on Americans' economic and <highlight>private</highlight> lives, not to mention infuriating.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它应该是：浪费时间拖累了美国人的经济和私人生活，更不用说激怒了。

examination_example.sentence: Citizens still have a right to expect <highlight>private</highlight> documents to remain <highlight>private</highlight> and protected by the Constitution's prohibition on unreasonable searches.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 公民仍然有权要求私人文件保持私密性，并受到宪法禁止不合理搜查私人文件的保护。

examination_example.sentence: Discussing the issue in <highlight>private</highlight> will make the powerful person feel less threatened.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 私下讨论这个问题会让有权有势的人感觉不到威胁。
